          "9.4":"9.4. In case of violation of intellectual property rights on Service, the respective rights holder undertakes to submit a pre-trial application to the Administration by e-mail. If the application is submitted by the authorized person, the copy of the document (in written or electronic form) confirming its credentials is attached to the application.",
